<div class="panel" id="about">
  <div class="container">

    <header class="page-header">
      <h3>Looking for work sucks.</h3>
      <h1>Let&rsquo;s make it suck less.</h1>
    </header>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="image">
        <%= image_tag("screenshots/post-listing-screen.png", :alt => "Post lisings") %>
      </div>

      <div class="large-text">
        <p>These days, job-hunting is basically a full-time job itself. Apparently the economy is in kind of rough shape.</p>
        <p>So if you&rsquo;re on the hunt, you probably end up sending out <em>hundreds</em> of resumes. That&rsquo;s an awful lot of names and details to remember. If you land an interview and the posting&rsquo;s been taken down, what do you do?</p>
        <p><strong>How do you keep track of it all?</strong></p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="large-text">
      <p>Suitor was built to help make your job hunt easier. Want to <strong>track deadlines &amp; interviews</strong>? <em>Done.</em> Need <strong>reminders to follow-up</strong> on an application? <em>You got &lsquo;em.</em> Just want to <strong>remember</strong> what you sent, who you sent it to, and when you sent it? <em>Okay.</em> How about <strong>visual indicators of your progress?</strong> Sure thing!
      </div>

      <div class="image">
        <%= image_tag("screenshots/add-job-post.png", :alt => "Add a job posting") %>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="image">
        <%= image_tag("screenshots/schedule-interview.png", :alt => "Schedule an interview") %>
      </div>

      <div class="large-text">
        <p>We&rsquo;ve got a lot more planned for Suitor&mdash;like social media and iCal integration, automatic email submissions, integration with existing job posting sites&mdash;down the line. The project is <a href="http://github.com/sarahsemark/suitor">open-source</a>, so contributions and bug reports are always welcome, and you can help us make it better. </p>
        <p><a class="jump" href="#signup">Want to <strong>give it a try</strong>?</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>


  </div>
  <a class="next jump" href="#signup"><i class="icon-arrow-down9"><span>Next panel</span></i></a>
</div>




<div class="panel" id="signup">
  <div class="container">

    <header class="page-header">
      <h3>Things are still in a bit of a state, but we're testing.</h3>
      <h1>You want in?</h1>
    </header>

    <div class="large-text">
      <p>Want to take it for a spin? We&rsquo;re looking for beta testers for our private beta (which is actually an alpha, but no need to quibble over Greek letters). If you&rsquo;ve got a lot of opinions that you&rsquo;d like to share, enter your information below, and we&rsquo;ll get back to you as soon as there&rsquo;s a slot available for you!</p>
    </div>

    <form action="//triggersandsparks.us1.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=7cf7b38d641914fc60e63954f&amp;id=2c3bb4988b" method="post" id="mc-embedded-subscribe-form" name="mc-embedded-subscribe-form" class="validate" target="_blank" novalidate>

      <fieldset class="primary">
        <h3>Let me try it out!</h3>
          <label for="mce-EMAIL">Email Address</label>
          <input type="email" placeholder="Cross our fingers, no spam." value="" name="EMAIL" class="required email" id="mce-EMAIL">

          <input type="submit" value="Get your invite" name="subscribe" id="mc-embedded-subscribe">
        </fieldset>
    </form>
  </div>
</div>


